1. Clone https://github.com/BlokasLabs/linux-debian.git
2. Build v6, v7, v7l, v8, 2712 flavours according to the link below:

	https://wiki.debian.org/HowToCrossBuildAnOfficialDebianKernelPackage


Updating the kernel:

* Use env_setup.sh to download original kernel based on RPi firmware / kernel commit.
* Use gen_patch.sh to generate a rpi.patch file to be placed in linux-debian.
